WEBVTT

00:02:29.784 --> 00:02:32.711
Now, to ruminate means to chew over.

00:02:33.014 --> 00:02:36.185
The word refers
to how cows digest their food.

00:02:37.090 --> 00:02:41.217
For those of you unfamiliar
with the joys of cow digestion,

00:02:41.241 --> 00:02:42.787
cows chew,

00:02:42.811 --> 00:02:44.082
then they swallow,

00:02:44.106 --> 00:02:47.118
then they regurgitate it back up
and chew it again.

00:02:47.142 --> 00:02:48.231
(Laughter)

00:02:48.255 --> 00:02:49.415
It's disgusting.

00:02:49.439 --> 00:02:50.446
(Laughter)

00:02:50.470 --> 00:02:51.938
But it works for cows.

00:02:51.962 --> 00:02:52.998
(Laughter)

00:02:53.022 --> 00:02:55.419
It does not work for humans.

00:02:55.443 --> 00:02:58.736
Because what we chew over
are the upsetting things,

00:02:58.760 --> 00:03:00.434
the distressing things,